er. -->\n\t<h3 class=\"ea-header\">\n\t\t<!-- Add anchor tag for header. -->\n\t\t<a class=\"collapsed\" id=\"ea-header-103151\" role=\"button\" data-sptoggle=\"spcollapse\" data-sptarget=\"#collapse103151\" aria-controls=\"collapse103151\" href=\"#\"  aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">\n\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"presentation\" class=\"ea-expand-icon eap-icon-ea-expand-plus\"><\/i> Hint ya\u011f\u0131 sa\u00e7\u0131 sertle\u015ftirir mi?\t\t<\/a> <!-- Close anchor tag for header. -->\n\t<\/h3>\t<!-- Close header tag. -->\n\t<!-- Start collapsible content div. -->\n\t<div class=\"sp-collapse spcollapse \" id=\"collapse103151\" data-parent=\"#sp-ea-10315\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"ea-header-103151\">  <!-- Content div. -->\n\t\t<div class=\"ea-body\">\n\t\t<p><span><\/span>Hay\u0131r, di\u011fer ya\u011flarla kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131nda sertle\u015fme yapmaz.<span>\u00a0<\/span><strong>Hindistancevizi ve argan ya\u011f\u0131<\/strong><span>\u00a0<\/span>ile dengelenerek sa\u00e7\u0131 yumu\u015fat\u0131r.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div> <!-- Close content div. -->\n\t<\/div> <!-- Close collapse div. -->\n<\/div> <!-- Close card div. -->\n<!-- Start accordion card div. -->\n<div class=\"ea-card  sp-ea-single\">\n\t<!-- Start accordion header. -->\n\t<h3 class=\"ea-header\">\n\t\t<!-- Add anchor tag for header. -->\n\t\t<a class=\"collapsed\" id=\"ea-header-103152\" role=\"button\" data-sptoggle=\"spcollapse\" data-sptarget=\"#collapse103152\" aria-controls=\"collapse103152\" href=\"#\"  aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">\n\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"presentation\" class=\"ea-expand-icon eap-icon-ea-expand-plus\"><\/i> U\u00e7ucu ya\u011flar alerji yapar m\u0131?\t\t<\/a> <!-- Close anchor tag for header. -->\n\t<\/h3>\t<!-- Close header tag. -->\n\t<!-- Start collapsible content div. -->\n\t<div class=\"sp-collapse spcollapse \" id=\"collapse103152\" data-parent=\"#sp-ea-10315\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"ea-header-1